{
  "stem": "7592.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He knew people from before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, how you doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This, this.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He came to me with a strange face to him, because I was in the [NON-ENGLISH], where was his factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He says, you come from where?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I said, from Madritsch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He's got a hobby-- he threw butts of cigarettes on the floor, so he could pick up later.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He got some tobacco.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he found out that I am from Madritsch, he took the butts, and with his shoes squeezed it so I couldn't pick it up.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If this is the reason, because he figured out we come over, then we're going to give him some money or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he treated us, the 15 families, very bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So this was my experience with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he find out I'm from Madritsch, he step on the butts so I couldn't pick it up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Besides this, I had no-- no business with him, because he's got his own people over there, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then he's got this-- another-- SS man who took care of the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- Who was that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Leopold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he couldn't be good, because, no, he wouldn't be SS running the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what  I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let me give you an example.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When people were stealing potatoes, they were in the ground, you know, for winter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he caught a few guys stealing potatoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know what he did?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took them and put them in the middle of the working place, put a big potato in his mouth, open.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he kept him for 24 hours like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Saliva was running over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was green and blue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I saw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then if, you know, he didn't like you, slap you in the face or something.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
